	er / $7 nonmember (per child\, per class)Ages 18 months to 3 years \n\n\n\
	nEach child must be accompanied by their guardian. Siblings are welcome to
	 attend but must be registered to participate. \n\n\n\nFamily Tree Members
	hip level and above required for member discount. \n\n\n\nJoin us for a we
	ekly story time featuring some of our favorite animals! Each week we will 
	read a nature-themed book\, observe biofacts and/or live animals\, and the
	n venture out on the trails for a self-guided hike. \n\n\n\nSummer Childre
	n’s Program registration will open Tuesday\, February 3\, 2026 for Arboret
	um Members. Nonmember registration will open Tuesday\, February 10\, 2026.
